title: NNPACK build issue
body_html:
I pulled the code from the main branch today and still got this error:

[ 91%] Linking CXX executable wrapdim_test
../libATen.so.1: undefined reference to `nnp_convolution_kernel_gradient'

I checked that the nnp_convolution_kernel_gradient is present in the libnnpack.so in /usr/local/lib on my system.

When I pulled the change in #4439, I got a little bit further in compilation (the wrapdim_test compiled ok) , but still got this:

[ 93%] Linking CXX executable undefined_tensor_test
../libATen.so.1: undefined reference to `nnp_convolution_kernel_gradient'

So, the build still seems to be broken with the NNPACK support.
